argin-bottom: 0px !important; vertical-align: inherit;\">tho&aacute;t</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; vertical-align: inherit;\"> (</span></span><span class=\"pl-c1\" style=\"color: #0086b3;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; vertical-align: inherit;\"> 0</span></span></span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; vertical-align: inherit;\"> ); </span></span><span class=\"pl-c\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px !important; color: #969896;\"><span class=\"pl-c\" style=\"margin-top: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; vertical-align: inherit;\">//</span></span></span><span style=\"margin-bottom: 0px !important; vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; vertical-align: inherit;\"> Tho&aacute;t khỏi quy tr&igrave;nh PHP hiện tại.</span></span></span></span></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em;\"><span style=\"margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 0px !important; vertical-align: inherit;\">Bạn cần viết lại m&aacute;y chủ của m&igrave;nh để phản hồi lại một điểm cuối cụ thể</span></p>\r\n</article>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"gh-btn-container\" style=\"text-align: center; padding: 0.1em 0px 1.15em; box-shadow: #ffffff 0px 0px 60px 42px; position: relative; z-index: 100;\"><a class=\"gh-btn\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; background-color: #f1f8ff; border-radius: 3px; line-height: 20px; padding: 0.28em 1.2em; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 0.75em; font-weight: bold; border: 1px solid #0366d6; color: #0366d6 !important;\" href=\"https://github.com/ankitpokhrel/tus-php\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Xem tr&ecirc;n GitHub</span></span></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<blockquote style=\"border-left: calc(0.2vw + 2px) solid #333333; padding: 0.71875px 43.2813px 0.71875px 28.8594px; margin: 1.6em 1vw; font-size: 0.92em; line-height: 1.4em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong>Cập nhật</strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;: Vimeo hiện đang sử dụng&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://github.com/ankitpokhrel/tus-php\">TusPHP</a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;trong&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://github.com/vimeo/vimeo.php/releases/tag/3.0.0\">v3</a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;của&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://github.com/vimeo/vimeo.php/pull/186\">thư viện PHP ch&iacute;nh thức</a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;của họ&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://github.com/vimeo/vimeo.php/pull/186\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">cho API Vimeo</span></a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;.</span></span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h2 style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 1.7em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.14em; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: #0a0a0a;\"><a class=\"anchor\" style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none; padding-top: 50px; margin-top: -50px; display: block; visibility: hidden; background-clip: content-box;\" href=\"https://dev.to/konsole/resumable-file-upload-in-php-handle-large-file-uploads-in-an-elegant-way-4a84#creating-a-server-to-handle-our%C2%A0requests\" name=\"creating-a-server-to-handle-our%C2%A0requests\"></a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Tạo một m&aacute;y chủ để xử l&yacute; c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cầu của ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; c&aacute;ch một m&aacute;y chủ đơn giản tr&ocirc;ng như thế n&agrave;o.</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #29292e; color: #f8f8f2; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\">\r\n<pre class=\"highlight php\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 43.2813px 14.4219px 43.2813px 64.9375px; font-size: 0.7em; border-radius: 0px; overflow-x: auto; color: #eff0f9; line-height: 1.42em; width: 800.969px; margin-left: -79.375px; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: auto; padding: 0px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: 0em; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"color: #75715e;\">// server.php</span>\r\n<span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$server</span>   <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">=</span> <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">new</span> <span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">\\TusPhp\\Tus\\Server</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">(</span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\'redis\'</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">);</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$response</span> <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">=</span> <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$server</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">serve</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">();</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$response</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">send</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">();</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">exit</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">(</span><span class=\"mi\" style=\"color: #ae81ff;\">0</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">);</span> <span class=\"c1\" style=\"color: #75715e;\">// Exit from current PHP process.</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Bạn cần cấu h&igrave;nh m&aacute;y chủ của m&igrave;nh để đ&aacute;p ứng điểm cuối cụ thể.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">V&iacute; dụ: ở Nginx, bạn sẽ l&agrave;m một c&aacute;i g&igrave; đ&oacute; như thế n&agrave;y:</span></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #29292e; color: #f8f8f2; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\">\r\n<pre class=\"highlight plaintext\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 43.2813px 14.4219px 43.2813px 64.9375px; font-size: 0.7em; border-radius: 0px; overflow-x: auto; color: #eff0f9; line-height: 1.42em; width: 800.969px; margin-left: -79.375px; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: auto; padding: 0px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: 0em; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em;\"># nginx.conf\r\n\r\nlocation /files {\r\n    try_files $uri $uri/ /path/to/server.php?$query_string;\r\n}\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Giả sử rằng URL đến m&aacute;y chủ của ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i l&agrave;&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"http://server.tus.local/\">http: //server.tus.local</a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">V&igrave; vậy, dựa tr&ecirc;n cấu h&igrave;nh nginx ở tr&ecirc;n, ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; thể truy cập c&aacute;c điểm cuối tus của m&igrave;nh bằng c&aacute;ch sử dụng&nbsp;</span></span><a style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"http://server.tus.local/files\">http: //server.tus.local/files</a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">B&acirc;y giờ, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i đ&atilde; theo c&aacute;c điểm cuối RESTful c&oacute; sẵn để l&agrave;m việc với.</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #29292e; color: #f8f8f2; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\">\r\n<pre class=\"highlight plaintext\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 43.2813px 14.4219px 43.2813px 64.9375px; font-size: 0.7em; border-radius: 0px; overflow-x: auto; color: #eff0f9; line-height: 1.42em; width: 800.969px; margin-left: -79.375px; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: auto; padding: 0px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: 0em; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em;\"># Gather information about server\'s current configuration\r\nOPTIONS /files\r\n\r\n# Check if the given upload is valid\r\nHEAD /files/{upload-key}\r\n\r\n# Create a new upload\r\nPOST /files\r\n\r\n# Resume upload created with POST\r\nPATCH /files/{upload-key}\r\n\r\n# Delete the previous upload\r\nDELETE /files/{upload-key}\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Kiểm tra c&aacute;c&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://tus.io/protocols/resumable-upload.html\">chi tiết giao thức</a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;để biết th&ecirc;m th&ocirc;ng tin về c&aacute;c điểm cuối.</span></p>\r\n<blockquote style=\"border-left: calc(0.2vw + 2px) solid #333333; padding: 0.71875px 43.2813px 0.71875px 28.8594px; margin: 1.6em 1vw; font-size: 0.92em; line-height: 1.4em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif;\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Nếu bạn đang sử dụng bất kỳ khung c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c n&agrave;o như Laravel, thay v&igrave; sửa đổi cấu h&igrave;nh m&aacute;y chủ của m&igrave;nh, bạn c&oacute; thể x&aacute;c định c&aacute;c tuyến đường đến tất cả c&aacute;c điểm cuối dựa tr&ecirc;n cơ sở trong tệp tuyến đường khung của bạn.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i sẽ đề cập chi tiết n&agrave;y trong một hướng dẫn kh&aacute;c.</span></span></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<h2 style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 1.7em; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.14em; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: #0a0a0a;\"><a class=\"anchor\" style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none; padding-top: 50px; margin-top: -50px; display: block; visibility: hidden; background-clip: content-box;\" href=\"https://dev.to/konsole/resumable-file-upload-in-php-handle-large-file-uploads-in-an-elegant-way-4a84#handling-upload-using-tusphp%C2%A0client\" name=\"handling-upload-using-tusphp%C2%A0client\"></a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Xử l&yacute; tải l&ecirc;n bằng ứng dụng kh&aacute;ch tus-php</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Khi m&aacute;y chủ đ&atilde; được đặt đ&uacute;ng chỗ, m&aacute;y kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; thể được sử dụng để tải l&ecirc;n một tệp theo từng khối.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Ch&uacute;ng ta h&atilde;y bắt đầu bằng c&aacute;ch tạo một biểu mẫu HTML đơn giản để nhận đầu v&agrave;o từ người d&ugrave;ng.</span></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #29292e; color: #f8f8f2; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\">\r\n<pre class=\"highlight html\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 43.2813px 14.4219px 43.2813px 64.9375px; font-size: 0.7em; border-radius: 0px; overflow-x: auto; color: #eff0f9; line-height: 1.42em; width: 800.969px; margin-left: -79.375px; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: auto; padding: 0px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: 0em; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span class=\"nt\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">&lt;form</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">action=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\"upload.php\"</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">method=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\"post\"</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">enctype=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\"multipart/form-data\"</span><span class=\"nt\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">&gt;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"nt\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">&lt;input</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">type=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\"file\"</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">name=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\"tus_file\"</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">id=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\"tus-file\"</span> <span class=\"nt\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">/&gt;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"nt\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">&lt;input</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">type=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\"submit\"</span> <span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">value=</span><span class=\"s\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\"Upload\"</span> <span class=\"nt\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">/&gt;</span>\r\n<span class=\"nt\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">&lt;/form&gt;</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Sau khi một biểu mẫu được gửi, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i cần phải l&agrave;m theo v&agrave;i bước để xử l&yacute; việc tải l&ecirc;n.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; color: #0a0a0a; font-size: 21px;\"><a class=\"anchor\" style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none; padding-top: 50px; margin-top: -50px; display: block; visibility: hidden; background-clip: content-box;\" href=\"https://dev.to/konsole/resumable-file-upload-in-php-handle-large-file-uploads-in-an-elegant-way-4a84#1-create-a-tusphp-client-object\" name=\"1-create-a-tusphp-client-object\"></a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">1. Tạo một đối tượng m&aacute;y kh&aacute;ch tus-php</span></h4>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #29292e; color: #f8f8f2; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\">\r\n<pre class=\"highlight php\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 43.2813px 14.4219px 43.2813px 64.9375px; font-size: 0.7em; border-radius: 0px; overflow-x: auto; color: #eff0f9; line-height: 1.42em; width: 800.969px; margin-left: -79.375px; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: auto; padding: 0px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: 0em; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"color: #75715e;\">// Tus client</span>\r\n<span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$client</span> <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">=</span> <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">new</span> <span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">\\TusPhp\\Tus\\Client</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">(</span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\'http://server.tus.local\'</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">);</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Tham số đầu ti&ecirc;n trong đoạn m&atilde; tr&ecirc;n l&agrave; điểm cuối m&aacute;y chủ tus của bạn.</span></p>\r\n<h4 style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; color: #0a0a0a; font-size: 21px;\"><a class=\"anchor\" style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none; padding-top: 50px; margin-top: -50px; display: block; visibility: hidden; background-clip: content-box;\" href=\"https://dev.to/konsole/resumable-file-upload-in-php-handle-large-file-uploads-in-an-elegant-way-4a84#2-initialize-client-with-file-metadata\" name=\"2-initialize-client-with-file-metadata\"></a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">2. Khởi tạo m&aacute;y kh&aacute;ch với si&ecirc;u dữ liệu tệp</span></h4>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Để duy nhất tải l&ecirc;n, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i cần sử dụng một số định danh để nhận ra tải l&ecirc;n trong c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cầu sắp tới.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Đối với điều n&agrave;y, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i sẽ phải tạo một kh&oacute;a tải l&ecirc;n duy nhất c&oacute; thể được sử dụng để tiếp tục tải l&ecirc;n sau n&agrave;y.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Bạn c&oacute; thể cung cấp kh&oacute;a tải l&ecirc;n một c&aacute;ch r&otilde; r&agrave;ng hoặc để hệ thống tự tạo một kh&oacute;a.</span></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #29292e; color: #f8f8f2; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\">\r\n<pre class=\"highlight php\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 43.2813px 14.4219px 43.2813px 64.9375px; font-size: 0.7em; border-radius: 0px; overflow-x: auto; color: #eff0f9; line-height: 1.42em; width: 800.969px; margin-left: -79.375px; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: auto; padding: 0px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: 0em; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"color: #75715e;\">// Set upload key and file meta</span>\r\n<span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$client</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">setKey</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">(</span><span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$uploadKey</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">file</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">(</span><span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$_FILES</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">[</span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\'tus_file\'</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">][</span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\'tmp_name\'</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">],</span> <span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\'your file name\'</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">);</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Nếu bạn kh&ocirc;ng cung cấp kh&oacute;a tải l&ecirc;n một c&aacute;ch r&otilde; r&agrave;ng, bước tr&ecirc;n sẽ giống như thế n&agrave;y:</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #29292e; color: #f8f8f2; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\">\r\n<pre class=\"highlight php\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 43.2813px 14.4219px 43.2813px 64.9375px; font-size: 0.7em; border-radius: 0px; overflow-x: auto; color: #eff0f9; line-height: 1.42em; width: 800.969px; margin-left: -79.375px; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: auto; padding: 0px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: 0em; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$client</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">file</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">(</span><span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$_FILES</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">[</span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\'tus_file\'</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">][</span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\'tmp_name\'</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">],</span> <span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\'your file name\'</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">);</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$uploadKey</span> <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">=</span> <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$client</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">getKey</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">();</span> <span class=\"c1\" style=\"color: #75715e;\">// Unique upload key</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4 style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; color: #0a0a0a; font-size: 21px;\"><a class=\"anchor\" style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none; padding-top: 50px; margin-top: -50px; display: block; visibility: hidden; background-clip: content-box;\" href=\"https://dev.to/konsole/resumable-file-upload-in-php-handle-large-file-uploads-in-an-elegant-way-4a84#3-upload-a-chunk\" name=\"3-upload-a-chunk\"></a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">3. Tải l&ecirc;n một đoạn</span></h4>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #29292e; color: #f8f8f2; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\">\r\n<pre class=\"highlight php\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 43.2813px 14.4219px 43.2813px 64.9375px; font-size: 0.7em; border-radius: 0px; overflow-x: auto; color: #eff0f9; line-height: 1.42em; width: 800.969px; margin-left: -79.375px; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: auto; padding: 0px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: 0em; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span class=\"c1\" style=\"color: #75715e;\">// $chunkSize is size in bytes, i.e. 5000000 for 5 MB</span>\r\n<span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$bytesUploaded</span> <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">=</span> <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$client</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">upload</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">(</span><span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$chunkSize</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">);</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Lần tới, khi bạn muốn tải l&ecirc;n một', '04-01-2019');
INSERT INTO `post` (`idpost`, `idcategory`, `idadmin`, `title`, `slug`, `images`, `content`, `created`) VALUES
(9, 6, 'TuanIT', 'Nhận giải pháp cho lỗi Laravel ngay trong dấu vết ngăn xếp.', 'nhan-giai-phap-cho-loi-laravel-ngay-trong-dau-vet-ngan-xep', '89m4zopz2bkyxjblix48.PNG', '<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><a class=\"article-body-image-wrapper\" style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: zoom-in;\" href=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--ksELfsqo--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://thepracticaldev.s3.amazonaws.com/i/89m4zopz2bkyxjblix48.PNG\"><img style=\"height: auto; position: relative; display: block; margin: auto; left: -6px; max-width: calc(100% + 12px);\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--ksELfsqo--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://thepracticaldev.s3.amazonaws.com/i/89m4zopz2bkyxjblix48.PNG\" alt=\"laravel-errorAndSolution\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><strong>Nhận giải ph&aacute;p cho c&aacute;c lỗi l&agrave; một trong những th&aacute;ch thức lớn khiến t&ocirc;i mất nhiều thời gian l&agrave;m người học với nền tảng nghệ thuật.&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">T&igrave;nh huống n&agrave;y c&oacute; thể &aacute;p dụng cho nhiều nh&agrave; ph&aacute;t triển kh&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n cầu, v&igrave; vậy t&ocirc;i c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhiệm gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c nh&agrave; ph&aacute;t triển, đặc biệt l&agrave; người mới bắt đầu, t&igrave;m giải ph&aacute;p cho c&aacute;c lỗi kh&aacute;c nhau một c&aacute;ch dễ d&agrave;ng.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Người ta thường t&igrave;m kiếm c&aacute;c giải ph&aacute;p cho c&aacute;c lỗi một c&aacute;ch ngẫu nhi&ecirc;n với hy vọng t&igrave;m ra một giải ph&aacute;p - đ&ocirc;i khi - tốn rất nhiều thời gian v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng sức của c&aacute;c nh&agrave; ph&aacute;t triển.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Đ&oacute; r&otilde; r&agrave;ng kh&ocirc;ng phải l&agrave; một điều xấu!&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Nhưng t&ocirc;i tin rằng thời gian của c&aacute;c nh&agrave; ph&aacute;t triển sẽ được bảo tồn ở một mức độ n&agrave;o đ&oacute; nếu giải ph&aacute;p hoặc li&ecirc;n kết đến c&aacute;c giải ph&aacute;p cho một lỗi nhất định đi k&egrave;m với lỗi đ&oacute;.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Đ&oacute; l&agrave; l&yacute; do tại sao t&ocirc;i x&acirc;y dựng&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://github.com/codingnninja/lerrors\">một g&oacute;i laravel</a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;cung cấp cho c&aacute;c nh&agrave; ph&aacute;t triển (đặc biệt l&agrave; người mới bắt đầu) si&ecirc;u năng lực để c&oacute; được c&aacute;c giải ph&aacute;p cho lỗi laravel ngay trong dấu vết ngăn xếp một c&aacute;ch dễ d&agrave;ng.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">G&oacute;i n&agrave;y chỉ c&oacute; thể giải quyết khoảng năm lỗi laravel hiện tại.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">T&ocirc;i vẫn đang sửa lỗi, v&igrave; vậy n&oacute; sẽ được đ&aacute;nh gi&aacute; cao nếu bạn c&oacute; thể gi&uacute;p tất cả c&ugrave;ng.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Tr&ecirc;n hết, cần c&oacute; quan điểm của bạn về c&aacute;ch l&agrave;m cho dự &aacute;n n&agrave;y tốt hơn.</span></p>', '04-01-2019'),
(10, 6, 'TuanIT', 'Khi PHP Framework Sucks Series: Bộ điều khiển logic kinh doanh miễn phí', 'khi-php-framework-sucks-series:bo-dieu-khien-logic-kinh-doanh-mien-phi', 'eycwqg7yhsop6oe37ek1.jpg', '<h3 style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; font-size: 1.32em; font-weight: 400; padding-left: 6px; padding-right: 6px; color: #0a0a0a;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Logic nghiệp vụ trong bộ điều khiển</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">H&atilde;y bắt đầu với Bộ điều khiển v&agrave; logic kinh doanh của bạn.&nbsp;</span><em>Quy tắc số một: Kh&ocirc;ng đưa logic kinh doanh v&agrave;o bộ điều khiển bằng bất cứ gi&aacute; n&agrave;o!&nbsp;</em><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Logic nghiệp vụ trong bộ điều khiển đặc biệt c&oacute; vấn đề v&igrave; bộ điều khiển thường xuất ph&aacute;t từ khung.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Ngo&agrave;i ra, khi họ mở rộng lớp tr&igrave;nh điều khiển cơ sở khung, họ thường biết qu&aacute; nhiều (container).&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Như t&ecirc;n của n&oacute;, logic nghiệp vụ l&agrave; m&atilde; của bạn m&agrave; bạn muốn sử dụng lại v&agrave; l&agrave;m cho độc lập với c&aacute;c thư viện v&agrave; khung.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">N&oacute; n&ecirc;n được ph&acirc;n t&aacute;ch v&agrave; đ&oacute;ng g&oacute;i tốt v&igrave; bạn c&oacute; thể gọi c&ugrave;ng một phương thức từ c&aacute;c nơi kh&aacute;c nhau.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Dưới đ&acirc;y l&agrave; v&iacute; dụ về&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: #557de8; text-decoration-line: none;\" href=\"https://symfony.com/doc/current/best_practices/controllers.html\">trang thực h&agrave;nh tốt nhất của</a><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;bộ điều khiển Symfony&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">:</span></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #29292e; color: #f8f8f2; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\">\r\n<pre class=\"highlight php\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 43.2813px 14.4219px 43.2813px 64.9375px; font-size: 0.7em; border-radius: 0px; overflow-x: auto; color: #eff0f9; line-height: 1.42em; width: 800.969px; margin-left: -79.375px; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: auto; padding: 0px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: 0em; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">namespace</span> <span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">App\\Controller</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">use</span> <span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">App\\Entity\\Post</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">use</span> <span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">Symfony\\Bundle\\FrameworkBundle\\Controller\\AbstractController</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">use</span> <span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">Symfony\\Component\\Routing\\Annotation\\Route</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">class</span> <span class=\"nc\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">DefaultController</span> <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">extends</span> <span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">AbstractController</span>\r\n<span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"sd\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">/**\r\n     * @Route(\"/\", name=\"homepage\")\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">public</span> <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">function</span> <span class=\"nf\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">index</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">()</span>\r\n    <span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$posts</span> <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">=</span> <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$this</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">getDoctrine</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">()</span>\r\n            <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">getRepository</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">(</span><span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">Post</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">::</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">class</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">)</span>\r\n            <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">findLatest</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">();</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">return</span> <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$this</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">render</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">(</span><span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\'default/index.html.twig\'</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">,</span> <span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">[</span>\r\n            <span class=\"s1\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">\'posts\'</span> <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$posts</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">]);</span>\r\n    <span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">}</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Ở đ&acirc;y, logic kinh doanh nằm ở một nơi kh&ocirc;ng ph&ugrave; hợp.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Thay v&agrave;o đ&oacute;, ch&uacute;ng ta n&ecirc;n c&oacute; một lớp trả về cho ch&uacute;ng ta những b&agrave;i viết mới nhất.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; thể gọi lớp đ&oacute; v&igrave; mục đ&iacute;ch đơn giản l&agrave; PostFromDatabase.</span></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #29292e; color: #f8f8f2; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\">\r\n<pre class=\"highlight php\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 43.2813px 14.4219px 43.2813px 64.9375px; font-size: 0.7em; border-radius: 0px; overflow-x: auto; color: #eff0f9; line-height: 1.42em; width: 800.969px; margin-left: -79.375px; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: auto; padding: 0px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: 0em; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">namespace</span> <span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">ExampleNamespace</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">class</span> <span class=\"nc\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">PostsFromDatabase</span>\r\n<span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"sd\" style=\"color: #e6db74;\">/** @var ManagerRegistry**/</span>\r\n    <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">private</span> <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$doctrine</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">public</span> <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">function</span> <span class=\"nf\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">getDoctrine</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">()</span>\r\n    <span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">return</span> <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$this</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">doctrine</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">public</span> <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">function</span> <span class=\"nf\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">__construct</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">(</span><span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">ManagerRegistry</span> <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$doctrine</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$this</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">doctrine</span> <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">=</span> <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$doctrine</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">public</span> <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">function</span> <span class=\"nf\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">getLatest</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">()</span>\r\n    <span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$posts</span> <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">=</span> <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$this</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">getDoctrine</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">()</span>\r\n            <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">getRepository</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">(</span><span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">Post</span><span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">::</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">class</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">)</span>\r\n            <span class=\"o\" style=\"color: #f92672;\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"na\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">findLatest</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">();</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">return</span> <span class=\"nv\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">$posts</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">}</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.95em 0px 1.2em; padding: 0.2em; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Kiểm tra cho lớp n&agrave;y, trong trường hợp n&agrave;y, l&agrave; đơn giản</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"highlight\" style=\"background: #29292e; color: #f8f8f2; font-family: Palatino, \'Palatino Linotype\', \'Palatino LT STD\', \'Book Antiqua\', Georgia, serif; font-size: 21px;\">\r\n<pre class=\"highlight php\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 43.2813px 14.4219px 43.2813px 64.9375px; font-size: 0.7em; border-radius: 0px; overflow-x: auto; color: #eff0f9; line-height: 1.42em; width: 800.969px; margin-left: -79.375px; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><code style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin: auto; padding: 0px; border-radius: 2px; font-size: inherit; vertical-align: 0em; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6em;\"><span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">namespace</span> <span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">ExampleNamespace</span><span class=\"p\" style=\"color: #f8f8f2;\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"k\" style=\"color: #66d9ef;\">use</span> <span class=\"nx\" style=\"color: #a6e22e;\">Doctrine\\Common\\Persistence\\ManagerRegistry<